===Books, prose===
===Drama===
* &quot;The First President&quot; (opera, 1936)
* &quot;A Dream of Love&quot; (1949)
* &quot;Tituba’s Children&quot; (1950)
* &quot;Many Loves&quot; (1959)
* &quot;The Cure&quot; (1960)
The above are collected in &quot;Many Loves and Other Plays: The Collected Plays of William Carlos Williams&quot; (1962)

===Translations===
