*Gammel, Irene. “The Poetic Feud of William Carlos Williams, Ezra Pound, and the Baroness”. &quot;Baroness Elsa: Gender, Dada, and Everyday Modernity&quot;. Cambridge, MA: MIT Press, 2002. 262-285
*Leibowitz, Herbert. &quot;“Something Urgent I Have to Say to You”: The Life and Works of William Carlos Williams&quot;. New York: Farrar, Straus and Giroux, 2011; 496 pages.
*Mariani, Paul, &quot;William Carlos Williams: A New World Naked&quot;. San Antonio, Trinity University Press, 1981; 874 pages.

